test_large_range:
assert [7, 8, 9] == [8, 9]
  At index 0 diff: 7 != 8
  Left contains one more item: 9
  Full diff:
  - [8, 9]
  + [7, 8, 9]
  ?  +++
test_even_range:
assert [14, 16, 18] == [16, 18]
  At index 0 diff: 14 != 16
  Left contains one more item: 18
  Full diff:
  - [16, 18]
  + [14, 16, 18]
  ?  ++++
